      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Older car in poor condition that runs and drives, but it needs work and should be approached as a budget driver or project. Expect noticeable cosmetic wear, interior wear, and deferred maintenance, with age-related issues and imperfections throughout. Best for someone who wants an inexpensive vehicle and is prepared to put time and money into it.",
