    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with excellent value for a budget-minded buyer. This vehicle is being offered as a practical option for someone who wants dependable basic mobility at a highly accessible price. It shows its age and is best suited for a driver comfortable with a well-used vehicle, but it remains a compelling chance to own for less than the cost of many monthly payments. Priced to attract serious value shoppers.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable runaround or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great chance to get behind the wheel without spending a fortune. It\u2019s being sold as a budget-friendly option and would suit someone practical who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC. If you want honest, inexpensive motoring with plenty of potential, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Shows cosmetic wear and age as expected, but the powertrain pulls well, starts up reliably, and the chassis feels like a good foundation for a daily, backup car, or light project. Mechanical basics are there, and it presents as an honest, usable vehicle rather than a dressed-up trailer queen. If you want affordable entry-level transportation with decent drivability and room to improve over time, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Honest wear, priced to move fast.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A scrappy, honest machine with plenty of character, this car has the kind of well-worn presence that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for someone who loves a hands-on project, needs an affordable set of wheels, or simply appreciates a vehicle with a story already written into it. There\u2019s a rugged charm here you can\u2019t fake\u2014something dependable in spirit, practical in purpose, and full of potential for its next chapter. If you\u2019ve been looking for a budget-friendly ride with personality, this one is easy to imagine making your own.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Honest, budget-friendly transportation with plenty of practical value left to offer. This vehicle is being advertised in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer seeking an affordable project, basic commuter, or inexpensive backup vehicle. A straightforward opportunity to get into a car at a very accessible price point.",
      "price": 4900.0,
