      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a simple, affordable set of wheels without breaking the bank? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transportation or a handy project to tinker with. It shows its age and has the usual wear you\u2019d expect, but it still has plenty of value for the right buyer. If you want an honest, inexpensive car at a fair price, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project car with a willing powertrain, responsive steering feel, and a chassis that still has plenty of life left for the right owner. Starts up, moves out, and offers a great foundation for someone who knows their way around maintenance or wants an affordable driver to sort and improve over time. Cosmetic wear and age-related needs are present, but the mechanical package has the kind of straightforward, serviceable character enthusiasts appreciate. If you want an inexpensive entry point with usable hardware and real potential, this one is worth a look.",
